    title: "Jurnal OJS 3",
    description: "Hosting jurnal ilmiah dengan Open Journal Systems",
    techDetails: [
      "OJS 3.x install & config",
      "Plugin DOI/Crossref",
      "SMTP email setup",
      "PDF viewer optimized",
